{"tid":87903,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"行山遇到狗你地會點？","createTime":"2017-01-20T07:59:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-02T16:19:45.000Z","uid":32572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d15cffa5637820409bc5b0919f3db19575783359","tid":87903,"uid":32572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T07:59:57.000Z","msg":"事咁的<br />\n可能前世殺得狗多<br />\n小弟由細到大就好驚狗<br />\n但我又好鍾意行山<br />\n最慘係山附近既路有好附野狗<br />\n佢地衝出黎吠真係驚撚到尻縮<br />\n行又驚佢地會咬 得一條路既時候更加on9<br />\n<br />\n所以想問下行開山既巴絲你地遇到野狗既時候會點做<br />\n同埋有冇d方法可以教下無撚用既細佬"},{"pid":"4217f9eb41d9f94b00843a86b596bc0d054c03d1","tid":87903,"uid":49457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:01:32.000Z","msg":"留名學野<br />\n<br />\n有次半夜行麥徑三段聽到狗叫即嚇到拗柴收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"795889932e4d4a9831e588fb79c48054705dc555","tid":87903,"uid":22974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:01:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea9f438a397a787de96f17b5ccfb6acc5f30eef7","tid":87903,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:10:37.000Z","msg":"如果你平時有踢開狗 佢地唔會無端端吠你 <br />\n或者你個氣勢唔夠強<br />\n最緊要望隻狗 唔好有彎腰望佢 佢會第一時間覺得你地位身份低佢 <br />\n正行直過同唔點望佢就冇乜大問題"},{"pid":"ec3aed9908e1c590fad11f8bbae93a7eaf0bda19","tid":87903,"uid":32572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:31:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你平時有踢開狗 佢地唔會無端端吠你 <br />\n或者你個氣勢唔夠強<br />\n最緊要望隻狗 唔好有彎腰望佢 佢會第一時間覺得你地位身份低佢 <br />\n正行直過同唔點望佢就冇乜大問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係佢彈出黎吠我 我唔撚望佢直行直過？<br />\n如果唔小心望左就要一直望住佢行過佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"622afcbf4784f9080aaf8060fec3864c368dce16","tid":87903,"uid":32572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:32:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名學野<br />\n<br />\n有次半夜行麥徑三段聽到狗叫即嚇到拗柴收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最鍾意行麥徑<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf921fa5af8a92afdf18c93210806ee49e20d562","tid":87903,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:37:24.000Z","msg":"野味"},{"pid":"f4b213f2d0a7108d280b49a9ceb23877d271153f","tid":87903,"uid":73293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:42:03.000Z","msg":"煮左黎食"},{"pid":"f990d2759871ce7c2816346adfcd3fe4503c68ca","tid":87903,"uid":45765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:43:34.000Z","msg":"冇眼接觸咁過就ok"},{"pid":"d6358645d0bffb19e827f494cc7dbd971f1a04c3","tid":87903,"uid":13512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:43:36.000Z","msg":"餵譚仔"},{"pid":"9c167d52a6a2585dbae565956c915863bdbaf779","tid":87903,"uid":27455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:49:17.000Z","msg":"唔好有眼神接觸, 真係有起事上黎既話就記得係咁打佢個鼻因為狗有好多神經都係個度"},{"pid":"8ecef1b229e484cede788b816ad919e0d3f2a0a7","tid":87903,"uid":45597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:56:48.000Z","msg":"扮狗嚇返佢"},{"pid":"95accee2cf16c40932e06ac7a581d9a57cab453f","tid":87903,"uid":54658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T09:03:12.000Z","msg":"話說有次踩單車 <br />\n無啦啦有狗衝出嚟吠我追我<br />\n嚇到即刻炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隻狗見我炒車都比我嚇親 <br />\n即刻走左<br />\n心諗做乜玩鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e022e5764dbc12d174b63defc85e66d2fea7cac","tid":87903,"uid":60153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T09:04:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dee0084e6eb411f9a354649e700225610cf2cddf","tid":87903,"uid":3818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T09:08:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQ6y76KEyjTxmRRN2d69jX9g5LYxsMinj9eKUXkN87R38?filename=X26U229.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX26U229.jpg&h=22772992&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f170ef8637ab340f77708d6848c206eb90e835e9","tid":87903,"uid":45872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T09:17:37.000Z","msg":"如果係乖唔吠個啲一定過去同佢玩<br />\n吠就唔理佢直行直過就得 唔好望佢唔好跑"},{"pid":"ac8335a70505c787885a27727102b2d54cdcbab7","tid":87903,"uid":32572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T11:36:07.000Z","msg":"好似好多位巴打都話唔好有眼神接觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n仲有冇高手可以分享下"},{"pid":"e9462043262dfd6ab49b83370262c1fd5c454c58","tid":87903,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T11:40:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似好多位巴打都話唔好有眼神接觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n仲有冇高手可以分享下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拎條狀既行山棒，大路近行山徑既狗都比人打過，見到類似形狀既野唔敢主動攻擊你。"},{"pid":"de551de5f9a6baa76847aa06c980291a9e11fce0","tid":87903,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T11:42:10.000Z","msg":"Save先"},{"pid":"fc06e9f9444951738c97109d31b122f8946babe2","tid":87903,"uid":11914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T11:56:07.000Z","msg":"撚佢奶肉球"},{"pid":"2b04a91ebd54ddf9463eea9928209a2a35fc7619","tid":87903,"uid":57523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T14:51:34.000Z","msg":"留名 全盛時期行一次山比狗追左3次"},{"pid":"3d18b4407ba917c5e037343c97e1154c4430724b","tid":87903,"uid":49279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T07:21:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"945954eaf3d601519080b69a7d94a85106c1f669","tid":87903,"uid":32572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T08:27:13.000Z","msg":"屌假期推下post先"},{"pid":"264704e4b324920b2952fcee570a5b841ed186bc","tid":87903,"uid":32572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T08:32:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" 