咁易架葉師傅</blockquote><br />\n吾你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cff071dcaae98aaa0f3e3c9c4377f817466c5b5d","tid":87903,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:36:57.000Z","msg":"我試過行山遇到一群狗係度吠 我直行直過行到佢哋身邊佢哋就靜落嚟<br />\n當然未必次次佢哋都唔會攻擊<br />\n如果佢哋想攻擊你最緊要用一隻手護住條頸 咬其他地方你最多皮外傷但一咬氣管/頸你就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另一隻手瞄住佢個鼻打落去"},{"pid":"8688ebb8fd0f8b1bbd734c7c8ec9891f2a305103","tid":87903,"uid":40310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:38:49.000Z","msg":"試過行山比狗追 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時會帶碌行山棍但嗰日冇。兩個入一路大聲喝佢一路行，完全唔敢走，怕佢以為可以放心咬<br />\n<br />\n好彩咩事都冇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"404575317a158f0ab7e810ddc35fbf3fbe303db6","tid":87903,"uid":32572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T19:24:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我試過行山遇到一群狗係度吠 我直行直過行到佢哋身邊佢哋就靜落嚟<br />\n當然未必次次佢哋都唔會攻擊<br />\n如果佢哋想攻擊你最緊要用一隻手護住條頸 咬其他地方你最多皮外傷但一咬氣管/頸你就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另一隻手瞄住佢個鼻打落去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打打過狗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eca8255f94198140a9c7f1e68505b96ec862dcc","tid":87903,"uid":32572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T19:25:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過行山比狗追 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時會帶碌行山棍但嗰日冇。兩個入一路大聲喝佢一路行，完全唔敢走，怕佢以為可以放心咬<br />\n<br />\n好彩咩事都冇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大聲喝佢地其實佢地會唔會驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"654910ea4e79ef27888798d27eb1aeffe7a1f2f0","tid":87903,"uid":32572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T19:26:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>kpbl定支行山杖行山</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但d狗見到你拎野唔會更加覺得你想攻擊佢 跟住衝黎咬你？"},{"pid":"856bf53492593ffddca041d0fedfcb9e14f8eaff","tid":87903,"uid":45055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T19:28:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話說有次踩單車 <br />\n無啦啦有狗衝出嚟吠我追我<br />\n嚇到即刻炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隻狗見我炒車都比我嚇親 <br />\n即刻走左<br />\n心諗做乜玩鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都係踩單車比狗追<br />\n仲要3隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一路大叫一路係咁踩 踩踩下佢地就冇跟黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf755e35f849433625c10c852871227d8aaee94","tid":87903,"uid":72477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T19:29:11.000Z","msg":"會叫新假期介紹下隻狗幾得意，介紹下個下幾靚<br />\n<br />\n咁就可以召集千百計既人踩冧座山，嚇走隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"629f3725565c031cbca9e9495be9ec02cb0324ec","tid":87903,"uid":72477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T19:29:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會叫新假期介紹下隻狗幾得意，介紹下<span style=\"color: red;\">座山</span>幾靚<br />\n<br />\n咁就可以召集千百計既人踩冧座山，嚇走隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"648b6dbd2619c51aa112c014713c14c97a71590a","tid":87903,"uid":32572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T19:32:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會叫新假期介紹下隻狗幾得意，介紹下個下幾靚<br />\n<br />\n咁就可以召集千百計既人踩冧座山，嚇走隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾撚好計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebe879e5bd9c3c6aec68144184e58d8a15371713","tid":87903,"uid":21222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T19:33:11.000Z","msg":"其實狗都係同你一樣淆底，不過佢扮到好惡咁岩你又驚咪輸左，唔好向住佢行當無野旁邊過，我敢打賭9成唔敢沖黎咬你。"},{"pid":"e3d7291b10b9b7880ca7e6f10527c834a7d7de48","tid":87903,"uid":10968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T19:35:52.000Z","msg":"有次唔知行左去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條路好窄<br />\n有兩隻狗好靜咁坐係到 似係瞓左<br />\n我同女朋友行<br />\n佢留意唔到有狗 仲繼續行 <br />\n我拉都拉唔切佢返轉頭 <br />\n兩隻狗就企返起身吠我地<br />\n本身想走 點知個兩隻野就跑上嚟想禽上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我擋住條女 我自己企係到唔郁 諗住隻狗咬我算 <br />\n點知兩隻狗走嚟聞左我幾下就吠我<br />\n咁我都知咩事架喇 我諗入左佢地地盤 <br />\n我就慢慢向後行 兩隻狗就望實我 <br />\n距離拖遠五米左右同條女就跑走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9d6bfe3e48d503d78ff1712da5cbd6b17418d36","tid":87903,"uid":4149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T19:47:29.000Z","msg":"試過行完山經一條車路出返去<br />\n點知撞到4,5隻狗係咁吠同追住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得返一條路既情況下唯有跑返回頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後仲call左警犬派左架警車接我地出返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74355263b22532882bdee6c01ff8e2993bda1c47","tid":87903,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T19:50:07.000Z","msg":"帶老納張相佢睇"},{"pid":"572312948e665ef4b211b9cf0e99f0a691f0d72a","tid":87903,"uid":45232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T19:51:33.000Z","msg":"兜路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"821fd430b3438685d96086c4cd797ca02be36f5b","tid":87903,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T19:51:57.000Z","msg":"上過防狗班<br />\n眼住佢+唔好背對佢<br />\n唔好跑<br />\n如果feel到佢準備撲埋嚟就開遮"},{"pid":"4afd27ad5912d38f3404901ae56639903b3a9841","tid":87903,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T19:53:24.000Z","msg":"call我老死納dee<br />\n認真帶碌野去 佢最吠唔敢咬"}]}